      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm looking at some rezoning stuff in portland. can u explain what the main differences are between R5 and RM5 zoning? specifically i need to know if a small corner grocery store would be allowed in an RM5 district or if there are strict limits on commercial use in those areas.",
